{
  "stem": "3820.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Left the goods that they made for them, and were escorted back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later on in the ghetto, when my Uncle Chaim was allowed-- when he started going by himself, he was allowed to go on his own.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is how he-- he would take different routes, because they felt that with the whole family in the ghetto, that they-- and him-- that they could-- in a way, I guess they became so-- so convinced that he wouldn't do anything, that they came to trust him after so many trips back and forth.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's when he was able to-- to contact-- speaking to the younger men in the ghetto, those that were able to-- to leave for a while-- one of the men that-- he said he needed a helper.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the helper never came back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this was one of the boys that also became a partisan.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But-- The area there was-- was not-- it was a small town type area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was not a big city, so for us, the news was very scarce.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we-- many ways, I felt isolated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Whatever stories that he would come back with were not privy to my young ears, and I don't remember too much of that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, when things were quiet, we played in the streets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there was a lady who took several of the children and would try to teach us to-- the alphabet, little songs, things like that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no school to speak of, but they-- they tried in many ways, each little group, to do something for the children.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember any of the stories, but I know that I had begun to learn to read and write.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
